1
00:01:32,610 --> 00:01:39,870
[Better Halves]

2
00:01:40,300 --> 00:01:42,870
[Episode 3]

3
00:01:46,729 --> 00:01:48,009
She just left your house.

4
00:01:48,009 --> 00:01:50,240
She'll definitely pass through
this road later.

5
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:51,270
Got it. Thank you.

6
00:01:52,380 --> 00:01:53,800
I'll be a little late tomorrow.

7
00:01:53,800 --> 00:01:55,150
Send the things over first.

8
00:01:55,150 --> 00:01:56,150
Here is the money.

9
00:01:56,490 --> 00:01:57,740
Well done.

10
00:01:57,810 --> 00:02:00,070
I'm the best Chief Matchmaker after all.

11
00:02:00,590 --> 00:02:04,590
Marriage Broker Deng of
the Official
Matchmaking Agency has been commissioned

12
00:02:04,590 --> 00:02:07,510
to help the Qi family's only son,
Qi Shaoheng...

13
00:02:07,530 --> 00:02:08,680
What are you doing?

14
00:02:09,259 --> 00:02:10,350
What are you doing?

15
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:13,680
Are you Marriage Broker Deng?

16
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:14,260
Yes.

17
00:02:14,310 --> 00:02:16,370
You went to my house

18
00:02:16,590 --> 00:02:17,520
and used your fancy words

19
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:17,579
to trick my mother
into giving you the contract.

20
00:02:17,579 --> 00:02:19,470
[Contract]

21
00:02:19,750 --> 00:02:22,000
So you're Mr. Qi.

22
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:24,110
I didn't use any fancy words.

23
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,310
I was telling the truth,

24
00:02:25,310 --> 00:02:26,310
am I right, Mr. Qi?

25
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:28,480
You're of age this year.

26
00:02:28,630 --> 00:02:30,280
You're the only son in the family.

27
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,820
After your father died,

28
00:02:31,850 --> 00:02:34,120
it was your mother who
supported the family alone,

29
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:34,600
right?

30
00:02:34,910 --> 00:02:35,500
So what?

31
00:02:36,720 --> 00:02:37,210
Listen.

32
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:39,520
I can be filial to my mother
without getting married

33
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:41,120
and run the family business.

34
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,320
I'm warning you.

35
00:02:42,940 --> 00:02:44,460
If people from the
Official Matchmaking Agency

36
00:02:44,460 --> 00:02:46,770
show up in my house again,

37
00:02:46,970 --> 00:02:48,600
let the one who got his leg broken

38
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:50,090
be a lesson to you.

39
00:02:50,110 --> 00:02:50,680
Do you understand?

40
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:51,650
Alright.

41
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:52,770
I got it.

42
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:57,590
Go back and tell your people from
the Official Matchmaking Agency.

43
00:02:57,590 --> 00:02:59,150
If any of you dare to
come to my house again,

44
00:02:59,150 --> 00:03:01,280
I'll beat you up.

45
00:03:01,490 --> 00:03:04,020
If there're two, I'll beat both of them.

46
00:03:08,820 --> 00:03:10,230
I'm so mad.

47
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:28,570
This devil is really cruel.

48
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:31,450
Although I have a grudge
against Aunt Deng,

49
00:03:31,450 --> 00:03:33,360
he shouldn't beat his elders.

50
00:03:33,540 --> 00:03:34,340
In my opinion,

51
00:03:34,550 --> 00:03:36,810
Qi Shaoheng doesn't want to get married,

52
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:38,090
but he has no choice.

53
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:41,720
It means that Mrs. Qi is anxious to
arrange a marriage for her son.

54
00:03:41,810 --> 00:03:44,400
But now that Marriage Broker Deng
lost the contract,

55
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,360
and Qi Shaoheng doesn't want

56
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:47,790
other matchmakers from
the Official Matchmaking Agency.

57
00:03:47,790 --> 00:03:49,400
Since there's no competition now,

58
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,310
isn't it a good time

59
00:03:50,310 --> 00:03:53,170
for you to fight for
the Qi family matchmaking case?

60
00:03:53,790 --> 00:03:54,790
That makes sense.

61
00:03:54,930 --> 00:03:55,660
What's next?

62
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:57,990
Well,

63
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:01,210
you don't need to worry
about Qi Shaoheng's fists.

64
00:04:01,210 --> 00:04:03,210
Because I'm more powerful than him.

65
00:04:04,910 --> 00:04:06,930
If you have the contract,

66
00:04:07,250 --> 00:04:09,310
Qi Shaoheng can't do anything to you.

67
00:04:10,330 --> 00:04:12,570
That's half the battle won, right?

68
00:04:13,180 --> 00:04:14,250
That makes sense.

69
00:04:14,590 --> 00:04:16,630
In that case, let's visit her in person

70
00:04:16,630 --> 00:04:18,160
and discuss it with Mrs. Qi.

71
00:04:18,730 --> 00:04:19,260
Let's go.

72
00:04:22,170 --> 00:04:22,910
Hurry up.

73
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:28,390
[Security]

74
00:04:28,470 --> 00:04:29,680
[Merging the world]

75
00:04:36,990 --> 00:04:37,620
Okay.

76
00:04:41,950 --> 00:04:42,090
Shi Fa'ke, right?

77
00:04:42,090 --> 00:04:43,860
[Weiyuan Escort Agency, Mrs. Qi]

78
00:04:43,860 --> 00:04:44,790
You're late.

79
00:04:44,990 --> 00:04:46,600
I've signed a contract with
Marriage Broker Deng

80
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:47,550
from the Official Matchmaking Agency.

81
00:04:47,550 --> 00:04:49,440
Besides, your family is still involved

82
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:50,650
in a case with my family.

83
00:04:50,650 --> 00:04:52,030
I'm not at liberty to discuss it with you.

84
00:04:52,030 --> 00:04:52,830
Please leave.

85
00:04:53,409 --> 00:04:54,470
No, Mrs. Qi.

86
00:04:54,490 --> 00:04:55,700
I'm here because...

87
00:04:55,730 --> 00:04:57,860
Madam, Marriage Broker Deng from
the Official Matchmaking Agency is here.

88
00:04:57,860 --> 00:04:59,060
Why is she here again?

89
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,390
Madam.

90
00:05:01,780 --> 00:05:03,710
You'll understand when you see it.

91
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,730
This bastard.

92
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,850
How dare he tear up my contract?

93
00:05:07,890 --> 00:05:11,040
Madam, it seems that
Mr. Qi is quite dissatisfied

94
00:05:11,070 --> 00:05:12,150
with Marriage Broker Deng.

95
00:05:12,150 --> 00:05:13,110
Shi Fa'ke.

96
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:15,940
You're the daughter of
the guilty Tao family

97
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:18,330
and you're involved in the Qi family case.

98
00:05:18,410 --> 00:05:19,240
I'm ordering you right now,

99
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:21,020
as the Chief Matchmaker of
the Official Matchmaking Agency,

100
00:05:21,020 --> 00:05:21,560
[Security]

101
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:22,720
to get back to the office

102
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,630
and organize the documents.

103
00:05:23,630 --> 00:05:24,030
You...

104
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:27,380
Mrs. Qi, Marriage Broker Deng
was unsuccessful.

105
00:05:27,380 --> 00:05:30,110
Why don't we let Marriage Broker Shi
give it a try?

106
00:05:30,970 --> 00:05:31,590
Madam.

107
00:05:31,710 --> 00:05:33,900
Marriage Broker Deng is old.

108
00:05:34,280 --> 00:05:37,090
I'm sure he wouldn't like her taste.

109
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:38,760
I have a suggestion.

110
00:05:38,890 --> 00:05:41,650
Why don't you let a young marriage broker
like me have a try?

111
00:05:41,650 --> 00:05:42,940
Maybe my taste

112
00:05:42,970 --> 00:05:44,770
will meet Mr. Qi's expectations

113
00:05:44,770 --> 00:05:47,180
and he would voluntarily
entrust me with his marriage.

114
00:05:47,180 --> 00:05:47,870
What a joke.

115
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,440
I'm experienced

116
00:05:49,470 --> 00:05:51,070
and I couldn't persuade Mr. Qi.

117
00:05:51,070 --> 00:05:52,400
Who do you think you are?

118
00:05:52,750 --> 00:05:55,310
Firstly, I'm young and have good taste.

119
00:05:55,650 --> 00:05:58,159
Secondly, I know many young ladies.

120
00:05:58,190 --> 00:06:01,150
Thirdly, I can talk to Mr. Qi.

121
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:02,010
You...

122
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:03,950
Enough.
Marriage Broker Deng, stop arguing.

123
00:06:03,950 --> 00:06:04,110
[Security]

124
00:06:04,110 --> 00:06:06,510
Actually, what this young lady
said makes sense.

125
00:06:06,510 --> 00:06:08,860
My son is very stubborn.

126
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:10,680
Since you've experienced a setback here,

127
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:13,010
I'm afraid he won't let you
be his matchmaker anymore.

128
00:06:13,010 --> 00:06:14,140
Madam, you're wise.

129
00:06:14,150 --> 00:06:15,220
Madam, no.

130
00:06:15,250 --> 00:06:16,430
Enough, you two.

131
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:19,720
Since you two are
so concerned about my son,

132
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:20,670
why don't you

133
00:06:20,750 --> 00:06:23,010
talk to my son in person?

134
00:06:24,110 --> 00:06:26,610
I'll pay for the tea

135
00:06:26,740 --> 00:06:28,900
for whoever he
agrees to give the marriage to.

136
00:06:28,900 --> 00:06:29,900
What do you think?

137
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:31,350
Thank you, Madam.

138
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:33,010
I'm going to find Mr. Qi now.

139
00:06:33,770 --> 00:06:36,170
If Marriage Broker Deng is worried,

140
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:38,770
you can just leave
the matchmaking case to me.

141
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,520
No need. I...

142
00:06:44,220 --> 00:06:45,250
have my own plan.

143
00:06:51,640 --> 00:06:52,190
Buns!

144
00:06:52,190 --> 00:06:53,030
[Fourth Archway]

145
00:06:53,030 --> 00:06:53,970
Hot buns!

146
00:06:53,970 --> 00:06:57,590
[Liu's Teahouse]

147
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,480
Madam Liu.

148
00:07:03,790 --> 00:07:04,490
Come.

149
00:07:06,150 --> 00:07:06,720
Here.

150
00:07:08,280 --> 00:07:08,920
Careful.

151
00:07:08,940 --> 00:07:09,540
Thank you.

152
00:07:15,810 --> 00:07:16,610
Brother Lu,

153
00:07:17,060 --> 00:07:18,030
this merchant

154
00:07:18,050 --> 00:07:20,040
was limping on his right leg

155
00:07:20,070 --> 00:07:21,140
when he was talking to
Qi Shaoheng yesterday.

156
00:07:21,140 --> 00:07:22,690
But his left leg is crippled today.

157
00:07:22,690 --> 00:07:24,550
Sure enough, there's a scam here.

158
00:07:24,670 --> 00:07:25,990
Ke has a good eye.

159
00:07:27,020 --> 00:07:28,150
Have you heard?

160
00:07:28,540 --> 00:07:29,930
Qi Shaoheng from Weiyuan Escort Agency

161
00:07:29,930 --> 00:07:32,110
is violent and often gets rough.

162
00:07:32,710 --> 00:07:34,080
You heard about that too?

163
00:07:34,080 --> 00:07:35,280
It's only been half a day

164
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:36,940
and it's already spread like wildfire.

165
00:07:36,940 --> 00:07:37,610
No wonder

166
00:07:37,780 --> 00:07:40,440
he's not young and
yet he refuses to get married.

167
00:07:40,530 --> 00:07:43,930
Qi Shaoheng only just tore
Marriage Broker Deng's contract

168
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:46,140
and there's such a scandal today.

169
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:49,140
Could Marriage Broker Deng be behind this?

170
00:07:49,810 --> 00:07:50,940
You can't be so sure.

171
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:53,400
We still don't know who started this.

172
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,050
Qi Shaoheng is here.

173
00:07:56,050 --> 00:07:57,860
He's the notorious Qi Shaoheng?

174
00:07:57,860 --> 00:07:59,390
[Liu's Teahouse]

175
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:00,140
Look.

176
00:08:00,490 --> 00:08:01,090
The usual.

177
00:08:07,990 --> 00:08:10,000
Mr. Qi, if you want to go home for tea,

178
00:08:10,190 --> 00:08:11,600
I can send it to your home.

179
00:08:12,150 --> 00:08:13,680
It's serene and light here.

180
00:08:13,880 --> 00:08:15,340
How could my home compare?

181
00:08:21,730 --> 00:08:22,640
Mr. Qi.

182
00:08:23,940 --> 00:08:26,070
I'm Shi Fa'ke from
the Official Matchmaking Agency.

183
00:08:26,070 --> 00:08:29,200
Mrs. Qi asked me to talk
to you about marriage proposals.

184
00:08:36,630 --> 00:08:37,390
Shaoheng.

185
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:42,620
Why did you splash water on me?

186
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:44,840
You forced me to do it.

187
00:08:45,610 --> 00:08:47,150
Sir, please don't.

188
00:08:47,180 --> 00:08:48,000
Calm down.

189
00:08:50,660 --> 00:08:52,620
I've never seen you before.

190
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:53,840
What's your name?

191
00:08:54,050 --> 00:08:55,570
Not only do I want to fight,

192
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:57,220
but I also want to touch...

193
00:08:59,880 --> 00:09:00,720
Qi Shaoheng.

194
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:03,230
Do you want me to expose
your true nature in public?

195
00:09:03,230 --> 00:09:03,910
Expose me?

196
00:09:04,950 --> 00:09:07,080
You should be exposing yourself to me.

197
00:09:13,870 --> 00:09:15,240
What are they talking about?

198
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:16,570
Will something happen?

199
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,650
I can't hear them.

200
00:09:18,670 --> 00:09:20,070
Should we separate them?

201
00:09:21,250 --> 00:09:22,240
I don't know.

202
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:24,210
You're not admitting defeat?

203
00:09:24,210 --> 00:09:24,940
I'm not.

204
00:09:29,820 --> 00:09:32,180
Why did Mr. Qi splash water on me?

205
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,750
It seems that the rumor
about his love for violence

206
00:09:33,750 --> 00:09:34,790
is true.

207
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:37,400
So the rumor must be true.

208
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:40,050
What should we do?

209
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:41,340
That's really scary.

210
00:09:41,340 --> 00:09:43,720
Brother Lu, forget it.

211
00:09:43,980 --> 00:09:45,840
There are too many people
who'll talk. Let him go.

212
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:47,220
Ke, are you okay?

213
00:09:47,780 --> 00:09:48,800
I'm fine.

214
00:09:50,100 --> 00:09:52,130
Qi Shaoheng, you'll regret it.

215
00:09:52,290 --> 00:09:53,080
Lu,

216
00:09:54,260 --> 00:09:55,320
I'll remember you.

217
00:09:55,350 --> 00:09:56,810
You'd better remember me.

218
00:09:56,880 --> 00:09:59,240
Alright, let's go.

219
00:09:59,770 --> 00:10:00,430
Let's go.

220
00:10:00,630 --> 00:10:01,360
Mr. Qi.

221
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:02,800
Well done.

222
00:10:03,030 --> 00:10:04,230
In just half a day,

223
00:10:04,260 --> 00:10:05,950
word about about my
perverse and violent temperament

224
00:10:05,950 --> 00:10:07,280
has been widely spread.

225
00:10:07,790 --> 00:10:08,870
Here's your reward.

226
00:10:08,870 --> 00:10:09,660
Thank you.

227
00:10:09,750 --> 00:10:12,200
The man who fought with me
at Liu's Teahouse today

228
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,130
is called Lu Chi.

229
00:10:13,550 --> 00:10:14,750
You just need to exaggerate it

230
00:10:14,750 --> 00:10:15,910
and spread the word.

231
00:10:16,040 --> 00:10:17,640
Mr. Qi, you're so demanding.

232
00:10:18,010 --> 00:10:19,470
Have you asked Lu about it?

233
00:10:23,160 --> 00:10:25,630
It's one thing to spend money
to spread rumors about yourself.

234
00:10:25,630 --> 00:10:26,900
Did Brother Lu offend you?

235
00:10:26,900 --> 00:10:28,710
You're dragging him down with you too.

236
00:10:28,710 --> 00:10:30,770
Tell me, did you bribe

237
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:31,910
the candied hawthorn vendor?

238
00:10:31,910 --> 00:10:33,280
And my former colleague.

239
00:10:33,280 --> 00:10:34,880
Did you pretend to break his leg

240
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:36,210
so he would work for you?

241
00:10:37,180 --> 00:10:39,240
Your Official Matchmaking Agency
is full of women.

242
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:40,410
He's the only man.

243
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:42,060
He wanted to quit long ago.

244
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:44,080
Isn't it a good thing that he's
of use to me then?

245
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:46,280
You tried so hard to deceive your mother

246
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,980
and refused all matchmakers.

247
00:10:48,790 --> 00:10:50,380
Is it because you already

248
00:10:51,570 --> 00:10:52,780
have someone in your heart?

249
00:10:52,780 --> 00:10:54,150
It's none of your business.

250
00:10:54,150 --> 00:10:55,710
Qi Shaoheng.

251
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:58,650
Looks like you did all this.

252
00:11:03,020 --> 00:11:05,440
Marriage Broker Shi, since you saw it,

253
00:11:05,630 --> 00:11:07,200
I'll tell you the truth.

254
00:11:07,260 --> 00:11:08,150
That's right.

255
00:11:08,340 --> 00:11:11,160
I like to beat people up.

256
00:11:11,270 --> 00:11:13,630
I think this young master
is quite skilled.

257
00:11:13,630 --> 00:11:15,940
Can you play with me?

258
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:19,980
Mr. Qi, people have
different personalities.

259
00:11:20,270 --> 00:11:22,400
But everyone has their strengths.

260
00:11:22,570 --> 00:11:24,450
No matter who you want to get married to,

261
00:11:24,450 --> 00:11:25,970
as long as you two love each other,

262
00:11:25,970 --> 00:11:27,350
I will be your matchmaker.

263
00:11:27,350 --> 00:11:28,480
But I'm warning you.

264
00:11:28,510 --> 00:11:30,530
Lu doesn't want to get involved with you.

265
00:11:30,530 --> 00:11:31,990
Don't tarnish his reputation.

266
00:11:31,990 --> 00:11:33,700
Sure,

267
00:11:34,030 --> 00:11:35,560
you could be my matchmaker.

268
00:11:35,680 --> 00:11:37,300
But I have to test you

269
00:11:37,430 --> 00:11:39,270
and see whether you are as snobbish

270
00:11:39,270 --> 00:11:41,060
as the people from
the Official Matchmaking Agency.

271
00:11:41,060 --> 00:11:41,860
For example,

272
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:44,900
what about witnessing
a marriage for my sister?

273
00:11:46,140 --> 00:11:48,170
Who does she want to marry?

274
00:11:48,390 --> 00:11:50,510
Ke, don't trust him so easily.

275
00:11:50,860 --> 00:11:51,640
Don't be afraid.

276
00:11:51,640 --> 00:11:53,320
I'm the best at witnessing marriages.

277
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:55,160
Whatever sister this is,
she'll be satisfied.

278
