found a suitable candidate.

558
00:22:13,470 --> 00:22:14,670
Why don't you tell us?

559
00:22:15,320 --> 00:22:16,240
Brother Lu,

560
00:22:16,350 --> 00:22:18,080
how could you ruin my matchmaking case?

561
00:22:18,080 --> 00:22:18,850
After all,

562
00:22:19,090 --> 00:22:21,620
it depends on whether Mr. Qi
is willing or not.

563
00:22:22,130 --> 00:22:23,850
But if I lose the matchmaking case,

564
00:22:23,850 --> 00:22:25,490
I'll lose my position
as a marriage broker.

565
00:22:25,490 --> 00:22:27,550
Then I'll entrust my marriage to you.

566
00:22:28,950 --> 00:22:29,840
Deal.

567
00:22:30,850 --> 00:22:32,760
I should definitely reveal it.

568
00:22:32,970 --> 00:22:34,770
But it's inappropriate

569
00:22:34,790 --> 00:22:36,850
to reveal the young lady's name in public.

570
00:22:36,850 --> 00:22:37,620
Mr. Qi,

571
00:22:37,970 --> 00:22:40,090
