572
00:22:40,110 --> 00:22:42,640
and hear what
Marriage Broker Deng has to say?

573
00:22:43,910 --> 00:22:46,310
Both of you,
please don't make a scene here.

574
00:22:46,600 --> 00:22:48,640
Although I'm anxious to
get my son married,

575
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:50,440
