576
00:22:50,990 --> 00:22:53,350
By the parents' command
and the words of the matchmaker.

577
00:22:53,350 --> 00:22:55,140
The parents' command comes first.

578
00:22:55,140 --> 00:22:56,490
You don't even know this.

579
00:22:56,490 --> 00:22:57,880
What right do you have

580
00:22:58,050 --> 00:22:59,780
to be a marriage broker, Shi Fa'ke?

581
00:22:59,780 --> 00:23:01,780
Of course I'll ask for your opinion.

582
00:23:02,280 --> 00:23:04,790
Madam, if you have any requirements,
please feel free to list them.

583
00:23:04,790 --> 00:23:06,460
We, a single son and widowed mother,

584
00:23:06,460 --> 00:23:09,190
have worked hard
to reach our current situation.

585
00:23:09,290 --> 00:23:12,110
A poor girl trying to climb to wealth
is absolutely not unacceptable.

586
00:23:12,110 --> 00:23:13,890
I do not seek nobility either.

587
00:23:13,910 --> 00:23:16,240
The social and economic backgrounds
just need to be compatible.

588
00:23:16,240 --> 00:23:17,300
What are you doing?

589
00:23:18,920 --> 00:23:20,180
This is your marriage.

590
00:23:20,520 --> 00:23:22,570
Mr. Qi, tell us.

591
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:24,670
Mr. Qi, you have to think carefully.

592
00:23:24,930 --> 00:23:26,030
Shi Fa'ke

593
00:23:26,050 --> 00:23:27,750
is just trying to get a matchmaking case

594
00:23:27,750 --> 00:23:30,210
to keep her position in
the Official Matchmaking Agency.

595
00:23:30,210 --> 00:23:32,020
And her mother

596
00:23:32,050 --> 00:23:35,510
is suspected of robbing
your family's property.

597
00:23:35,770 --> 00:23:36,350
Well...

598
00:23:37,490 --> 00:23:39,030
Mrs. Qi, Mr. Qi.

599
00:23:39,390 --> 00:23:40,650
My mother is innocent.

600
00:23:44,020 --> 00:23:44,800
Mrs. Qi,

601
00:23:45,250 --> 00:23:46,460
Shi Fa'ke

602
00:23:46,490 --> 00:23:49,480
instigated Mr. Qi
to ruin the Qi family's reputation

603
00:23:49,610 --> 00:23:52,640
and then came to witness
his horse's marriage.

604
00:23:52,930 --> 00:23:54,230
This person has evil intentions.

605
00:23:54,230 --> 00:23:56,230
She can't take the responsibility.

606
00:23:56,270 --> 00:23:58,310
